OL,3,CBBC boss says Trump has 'no basis' for
OL,4,Clegal action and vows to 'fight'
OL,6,FBBC chair Samir Shah has said Donald
OL,7,FTrump has "no basis for a defamation
OL,8,Fcase" and that they are "determined to
OL,9,Ffight" after the US president
OL,10,Fthreatened to sue the corporation.
OL,12,FIt comes after Trump said on Saturday
OL,13,Fhe plans to sue the BBC over the
OL,14,Fediting of his January 6, 2021 speech
OL,15,Fin a Panorama documentary, and will
OL,16,Fseek $1bn`$5bn (#758,600-#3.79bn) in
OL,17,Fdamages.
OL,19,FHe is expected to take legal action
OL,20,Fthis week.
