OL,3,CBBC boss says Trump has 'no basis' for
OL,4,Clegal action and vows to 'fight'
OL,6,FIn an email to staff seen by ITV News,
OL,7,FShah said: "There is a lot being
OL,8,Fwritten, said and speculated upon
OL,9,Fabout the possibility of legal action,
OL,10,Fincluding potential costs or
OL,11,Fsettlements.
OL,13,F"In all this we are, of course,
OL,14,Facutely aware of the privilege of our
OL,15,Ffunding and the need to protect our
OL,16,Flicence fee payers, the British public.
OL,18,F"I want to be very clear with you `
OL,19,Four position has not changed. There is
OL,20,Fno basis for a defamation case and we
OL,21,Fare determined to fight this."
