OL,3,CBBC boss says Trump has 'no basis' for
OL,4,Clegal action and vows to 'fight'
OL,6,FThe dispute stems from a Panorama
OL,7,Fepisode titled Trump: A Second
OL,8,FChance?, broadcast just days before
OL,9,Fthe 2024 US election.
OL,11,FThe third-party production company
OL,12,Fbehind the film spliced together three
OL,13,Fquotes from two parts of Trump's 2021
OL,14,Fspeech, making them appear as a single
OL,15,Fline in which he urged supporters to
OL,16,Fmarch with him and "fight like hell".
