OL,3,CBBC boss says Trump has 'no basis' for
OL,4,Clegal action and vows to 'fight'
OL,6,FIn his January 6 2021 speech, Trump
OL,7,Fsaid: "We're going to walk down to the
OL,8,FCapitol, and we're going to cheer on
OL,9,Four brave senators and congressmen and
OL,10,Fwomen."
OL,12,FMore than 50 minutes later, he added:
OL,13,F"And we fight. We fight like hell."
