OL,3,CBBC boss says Trump has 'no basis' for
OL,4,Clegal action and vows to 'fight'
OL,6,FIn the Panorama programme, the clip
OL,7,Fmade it appear like he said: "We're
OL,8,Fgoing to walk down to the Capitol...
OL,9,Fand I'll be there with you. And we
OL,10,Ffight. We fight like hell."
OL,12,FOther parts cut out were a section
OL,13,Fwhere Trump said he wanted supporters
OL,14,Fto demonstrate peacefully. Trump's
OL,15,Fdemand is that he be compensated for
OL,16,F"overwhelming financial and
OL,17,Freputational harm".
